1. Gathering the necessities
  Install Python from (https://www.python.org/downloads/)

2. Moving on
  Download the PasswordGenerator script as ZIP file
  Unzip the file and move the script to the desired folder 
  (This is where the Password Manager file will be created after running the script)

3. Running the script
  Double-click on the script to run it
  
4. Completing the process
  Enter the name of the site
  Enter the chosen username
  Script will generate a password for you, and save the entire information given to a file in the same folder
